TypeTeamMember.biography: Dan is the Vice President of the Core Engineering team at TripleLift. He's been at TripleLift since 2013 where he led the initial efforts to build out the real time bidding system. In a prior life he was the cofounder of a small startup that was acquired by an advertising agency and had a few stints as a quantitative engineer, including one on Wall Street during the 2008 financial crisis.
